  "title": "Testing & Commissioning Engineer (Construction, M&E)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate Testing &amp; Commissioning (T&amp;C) activities, ensuring quality, cost, and timeline adherence.</li>\n  <li>Plan, prepare, and execute T&amp;C activities, including documentation, software installation, and functional testing.</li>\n  <li>Conduct on-site testing with clients and contractors, troubleshooting system faults and recommending corrective actions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with corporate standards, industry regulations, and operational processes.</li>\n  <li>Support Quality Reviews and prepare reports on system performance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical/Mechanical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of relevant experience in Testing &amp; Commissioning in the <strong>Construction/M&amp;E industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong project coordination, organizational, and communication skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R1326740</p>",
